# Environment Variables Guide

This file documents the environment variables required for the project.

## Mercado Pago
- `MP_PUBLIC_KEY`: Your Mercado Pago Public Key (from the dashboard).

### Usage (Flutter)
When running or building the app, pass the `.env` file using `--dart-define-from-file`:
```bash
flutter run --dart-define-from-file=.env
```
Or for web builds:
```bash
flutter build web --dart-define-from-file=.env
```
